# ── API ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Backend API base URL (include the /api/v1 path)
#   Local dev:  VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:8000/api/v1
#   Render:     VITE_API_URL=https://vmf-v-1-api.onrender.com/api/v1
# Build behavior:
#   - `npm run dev` reads `.env.development` (use `.env.local` for local-only override)
#   - `npm run build:dev` uses `--mode staging` (deploy-safe)
#   - `npm run build:staging` uses `--mode staging`
#   - `npm run build:prod` uses `--mode production`
#   - staging mode falls back to `.env.production` unless `.env.staging` exists
#   - Optional override per command: BUILD_VITE_API_URL=<url> npm run build
VITE_API_URL=https://vmf-v-1-api.onrender.com/api/v1
